=Description=

"Perspegrity Solutions is a consulting service that works with organizations and groups, helping them '''embed their core values and ethics into their communication tools''', so that key values and human capacities are supported in day-to-day communication and collaboration.

The Perspegrity (pronounced Per-SPE-gri-ty) approach, geared to groups that make regular use of online collaboration software (such as web sites, discussion forums, wikis, distance learning environments, or decision support tools), is about much more than software. We take a human-systems approach to helping you configure and facilitate an online culture of higher quality communication, collaboration, and decision making.

Our unique methods support key collaborative capacities such as mutual regard, clarity, integrity, self-reflection, and multiple-perspectives. For organizations that value such ethics-oriented capacities and habits, ongoing support in the context of online work will supplement the agreements, trainings, and strategies that an organization uses to align decisions and actions with mission and core values."
(http://www.perspegrity.com/index.asp)


